-- Britain Sets World Record in Winning Women’s Pursuit Gold Medal
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-08-04T17:12:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-04/britain-sets-world-record-in-winning-women-s-pursuit-gold-medal.html
Britain won the women’s cycling team
pursuit gold in world record time at the London Olympics.  Dani King, Laura Trott and Joanna Rowsell finished in a
time of 3 minutes, 14.051 seconds to beat the U.S. in the final.
Canada took the bronze medal.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
